verbose_text: Bufalin, a major bufadeinolide like cardiac glycoside isolated from the skin and parotid venom glands of the toad, has been shown to induce cancer cell death through apoptotic pathways and has been investigted experimentally in a number of types of cancer.
evidence: Bufalin, a major bufadeinolide-like cardiac glycoside isolated from the skin and parotid venom glands of the toad              , has been shown to induce cancer cell death
